title: EA F1 Manager PC game - Game fix for Vista
description:
For Vista users having problems with EA F1 Manager for the PC

If you get an error when trying to run the game, or trying to run the game with the NO-CD patch, you need to add this file.

You add this file to the games directory, where all the install files are 
e.g. C:\Program Files\EA Sports\F1 Manager - place it in that folder (or wherever you installed the game)

Remember Vista and XP users - you may also need to use the NO-CD patch as the game was designed for Windows 98. NO-CD patch link - http://thepiratebay.se/tor/4143635

Enjoy!
